               <p>The case was stated by Mr. Walford.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18081130-23-person235">
                  ISAAC 
                  MARSH
               <interp inst="t18081130-23-person235" type="surname" value="MARSH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18081130-23-person235" type="given" value="ISAAC"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18081130-23-person235" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Q. What are you - A. I am a <rs id="t18081130-23-viclabel125" type="occupation">carrier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18081130-23-victim227 t18081130-23-viclabel125"></join>
